sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant API
    participant Firestore
    participant MediaWorker
    participant GCS

    User->>Frontend: Upload video file
    Frontend->>API: Request signed URL
    API-->>Frontend: Signed URL
    Frontend->>GCS: Upload to GCS

    Frontend->>API: Create video + media job
    API->>Firestore: Store job (status: pending)
    API-->>Frontend: Return job_id

    loop Poll for jobs
        MediaWorker->>Firestore: Get pending job
        MediaWorker->>GCS: Download video
        MediaWorker->>MediaWorker: Compress + Extract audio + Metadata
        MediaWorker->>GCS: Upload results
        MediaWorker->>Firestore: Update job (completed)
    end

    Frontend->>API: Poll job status
    API->>Firestore: Get job details
    API-->>Frontend: Status + results
    Frontend-->>User: Show complete
